
WWW::MakeAShorterLink
---------------------

NAME

  WWW::MakeAShorterLink

DESCRIPTION

  WWW::MakeAShorterLink is a perl module which provides an interface to
  makeashorterlink.com.

INSTALLATION

  To install this module type the following:

       perl Makefile.PL
       make
       make test
       make install

DEPENDENCIES

  This module requires the LWP bundle of modules.

